{"tid":2298949,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「達哥」送PS5予血癌病童","createTime":"2020-11-24T11:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T15:53:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"45d82d2ce940378d5c20150e8236fd4aafa98377","tid":2298949,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】好人好事，從不嫌多，英超般尼後衛達哥夫斯基最近就做了大好人。<br />\n今年28歲的達哥夫斯基（James Tarkowski）最近自掏腰包，購買兩部最新面世的PS5遊戲機給患上白血病的兒童及其好友。<br />\n<br />\nPS5每部遊戲機價值450鎊，有錢都未必買到，但該名英格蘭後衛大破慳囊，贈給10歲的軒捷臣和9歲的沙維。<br />\n<br />\n10歲的軒捷臣患上白血病，本身是是般尼球迷，將要接受3年治療，老友沙維就耗時50日跑了62英里，希望為前者籌集醫藥費，事件曝光後引起達哥夫斯基的關注。<br />\n<br />\n「非常震驚，我以為他只是來打招呼，想不到之後他回去車內拿出兩部PS5，送給我們。」沙維透露達哥夫斯基所做的好事。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"44702bf296fa7e4f4131d448aee554e567a440d3","tid":2298949,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"达哥要玩原神 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f9996fd4de226aeef7a541b0f6cab5fd4a9aeb","tid":2298949,"uid":55991,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"以為係达哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9a1ca3dbf358ec056f24675e156a7d592a69e9","tid":2298949,"uid":70439,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"以為达狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8e3b060e8db9a9e1a290c2997aa0401a475b69","tid":2298949,"uid":61604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"沙維<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e4ea8527390a16e97b8c429c67f2b02d366614","tid":2298949,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"中伏"},{"pid":"3f20ca22f2419fcbfce0df3c80269549c1071b05","tid":2298949,"uid":294953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:27